            <title>[SHIRO-577] Regression - Unable to set custom SessionValidationScheduler</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SHIRO-577</link>
                <project id="12310950" key="SHIRO">Shiro</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This was introduced by &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SHIRO-443&quot; title=&quot;SessionValidationScheduler created multiple times, enabling it is not thread safe&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SHIRO-443&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SHIRO-443&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, while making initialization of the sessionValidationScheulder thread safe.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Reported by user on mailing list:&lt;br/&gt;
